                              <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3464"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_huber_SB_CD_00613"><roleName type="title">Maister</roleName> Hanns Huber,
                                                  <roleName type="prof">licenciat geistlicher
                                                  rechten</roleName>
                                                <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_peter-altar_st_maria-messe_straiherin"><add>Kaplan</add></roleName></rs>,</rs>
                                    <triggerstring n="disp">bestätigt, dass</triggerstring>
                                    <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien">Bürgermeister und Rath</rs></rs> ihm <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_peter-altar_st_maria-messe_straiherin">die Messe, so weilent frau Klar die Straiherinn in
